{"tid":1304244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘開大片！油塘開大片！連登仔吹雞啊！","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:34:30.000Z","uid":11055,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9603d352578904eb857cf73797eec8f526a886b","tid":1304244,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"有眼耳口鼻既即刻蒲頭！"},{"pid":"ac972bc975f2ffb72f8a58e7831dee642ba8f23c","tid":1304244,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"形勢已經開始轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯開始分左兩批人仕"},{"pid":"e3f5f562eb2a2c93cd36581d8e18397a89a4e92b","tid":1304244,"uid":213379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請 停 止 濫 開 有 關 連 儂 牆 同 抵 制 T V B 既 P O S T</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304231</a>"},{"pid":"423705cc20c2e88febd0ac7c6a5f594e08e78e9f","tid":1304244,"uid":167559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"54687c1a8a98f88b311081cf95a44332b43ccfad","tid":1304244,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac972bc975f2ffb72f8a58e7831dee642ba8f23c","tid":1304244,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"形勢已經開始轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯開始分左兩批人仕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/16676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/16676</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8159d69a230b2a3f4cd3bcaf6ef628780b1f7b","tid":1304244,"uid":265972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"俾廢老搞事時，如果佢地出手打人，係咪可以合力制服佢地， 一路拍片一路大聲講行使緊市民拘捕權<br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第一○一（二）條，任何人可毋須手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人。不過，市民若要行使拘捕權，須遵守一些限制。<br />\n<br />\n        限制一：只可向觸犯了「可逮捕罪行」的人行使。按《釋義及通則條例》第三條，「可逮捕罪行」（arrestableoffence）是指法庭可判處超過十二個月監禁的罪行，例如強姦、非禮、盜竊、搶劫等。即是輕微罪行例如扔棄垃圾，便不是可逮捕罪行，大家無權拘捕垃圾蟲。<br />\n<br />\n        限制二：在行使拘捕時不可使用過份武力，在當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。<br />\n<br />\n        限制三：市民必須將被拘捕者交警員，在合理範圍內盡快將該人帶給裁判官依法處理。<br />\n<br />\n        例如，在「陳鎮坤案」（HCMA63/2012）中，超市女員工拘捕涉嫌非禮她的顧客。她當時不准被告離開，又在被告要逃走時追趕及捉住他，然後報案。法庭裁定該員工所用的武力合理，其拘捕合法。案中的小插曲是，裁判官竟然錯誤地認為「非禮」及「普通襲擊」均是可逮捕罪行。上訴庭指出，「普通襲擊」並不是可逮捕罪行，因為其最高判刑只是十二個月監禁。<br />\n<br />\n        一般人遇上罪案，可能難以分辨當時情況是否可以行使市民拘捕權。故此，大家在見義勇為拘捕了罪犯後，應該盡快交由警方處理，方為上策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.h1.com.hk%2Fdailynews%2Fheadline_news_detail_columnist.asp%3Fid%3D309147%C2%A7ion_name%3Dwtt%26kw%3D50&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=d4458e38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.h1.com.hk/dailynews/headline_news_detail_columnist.asp?id=309147&sect;ion_name=wtt&amp;kw=50</a>"},{"pid":"5021355e927b467a32b1e623c55a61303a95b10f","tid":1304244,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"257520693d69c711c57e053bd310aaa1f71319d8","tid":1304244,"uid":91314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70092ddf85ac6956bb4b6ad5edd4efe2f552913","tid":1304244,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"咩事"},{"pid":"341f181823d55a4b053a6451e68a47a97956dae5","tid":1304244,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"推 油塘嘅出曬來"},{"pid":"def0ac24fdd0247bf8c263b9c3bafb64139085bd","tid":1304244,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"其實已經有集中post<br />\n可唔可以集中討論嗰一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留返多啲位俾其他有用post"}]}